M|rio|| CTR (Meta) | > 1.5% | < 0.8% |
M|rio|| TikTok CPM | < $8 | > $15 |
M|rio|- **Lookalike source**: existing buyers (email list → Meta Custom Audience)
M|rio|- **Exclusions**: add-to-cart visitors who bounced more than 3 times (bargain signal)
M|rio|- **Retargeting window**: 14 days for website visitors; 30 days for video viewers
M|rio|- **Interest layer**: fashion, DTC, sustainable brands — avoid discount/deal seekers
M|rio|- UGC-style Reels outperform polished creative 2:1 on Meta
M|rio|- Model-focused cnt outperforms product-only flat lays
M|rio|- Hook must communicate product quality within 3 seconds
M|rio|- Carousel format works for multi-product storytelling
